beer.beer_description:
Fool Me Again

Last Christmas we brewed you a hazy, but the very next day you'd finished it and threw the can away. So this Christmas we're doing it all over again, this time with even more hops! Brewed with New Zealand grown wheat and malts and dry hopped with 11 different varieties. Fool Me Again is a giant fruit aroma explosion, loaded with mango, citrus peel, and dank resin. Happy Christmas from Garage Project.
beer.beer_style: IPA - Imperial / Double New England / Hazy
